ecules in a distorted form with a large amount of\nenergy after interaction and in the long run, oscillations of the light bullets\ngrow and the bullets become filaments. We have observed the same collision\ndynamics in both the negative and positive refractive index regimes of the\nmetamaterial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2022 16:58:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-08"}
