ent solution. For example, only training with a 80% sparse\ngenerator and a 70% sparse discriminator, our method can achieve even better\nperformance than the dense BigGAN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Mar 2022 15:18:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-08"}
